$response = find_redirect($complete_url,$req_header_hashTable);

if ( $response != 0 ){
      http.redirect($response);
}
else{
    $response = $complete_url;
}

}

sub find_redirect($requested_url,$hash_array){
   $local_search = $hash_array[$requested_url];
      
   if ($local_search)
      return $local_search;
   else
      return 0;
}

sub find_redirect($requested_url,$hash_array){
   $local_search = $hash_array[$requested_url];
      
   if ($local_search)
      return $local_search;
   else
      return 0;
}

sub find_redirect($requested_url,$hash_array){
   $local_search = $hash_array[$requested_url];
      
   if ($local_search)
      return $local_search;
   else
      return 0;
}

sub find_redirect($requested_url,$hash_array){
   $local_search = $hash_array[$requested_url];
      
   if ($local_search)
      return $local_search;
   else
      return 0;
}
